www.agoda.com, www.rentalcars.com, www.kayak.com, and www.opentable.com, among others. We are not including the
information contained on our websites as a part of, or incorporating it by reference into, this Annual Report on Form 10-K. We
make available free of charge through the www.bookingholdings.com website our Annual Reports on Form 10-K, Quarterly
Reports on Form 10-Q and Current Reports on Form 8-K, and amendments to these reports filed or furnished pursuant to Section
13(a) or 15(d) of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, as amended (the "Exchange Act"), as soon as reasonably practicable after we
electronically file such material with, or furnish such material to, the SEC. These reports and other information are also available,
free of charge, at www.sec.gov. In addition, the Company's Code of Conduct is available through the www.bookingholdings.com
website and any amendments to or waivers of the Code of Conduct will be disclosed on that website.
