18.    ACQUISITIONS
In November 2021, the Company entered into an agreement to acquire global flight booking provider Etraveli Group for
approximately 1.6 billion Euros ($1.7 billion). Completion of the acquisition is subject to certain closing conditions, including
regulatory approvals.
In December 2021, the Company acquired all of the outstanding stock of Getaroom, a business-to-business distributor of
hotel rooms, in a cash transaction for $1.3 billion ($1.2 billion, net of cash acquired).
